  "description": "Normally when I talk about what I broadly categorize as \u0026ldquo;settler nonsense,\u0026rdquo; I do it through short posts, usually right after I\u0026rsquo;ve digested whatever the nonsense was. As I said earlier this week in a newsletter, I\u0026rsquo;m planning to stop doing that, and instead put together a weekly look at what settler nonsense I saw through the week. This week I wasn\u0026rsquo;t on the computer too much, and still ended up with around twenty-five instances of nonsense.\n",
